gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 115, Timberwolves 112
gameRecap.excerpt: Nikola Jokic leads the Nuggets with 35 points and 16 rebounds to lead the Nuggets over the Timberwolves, 115-112. Michael Porter Jr. (26 points, four 3PT FG) and Jamal Murray (18 points, 11 assists) added a combined 44 points in the victory, while Anthony Edwards tallied 30 points, eight rebounds and eight assists for the Timberwolves in the losing effort. The Nuggets improve to 48-21 on the season, while the Timberwolves fall to 47-22.
